VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT \.Append\(.*HttpContext\.Current\.Request\.QueryString
WHEN EXPR MISSING:(HtmlEncode|UrlEncode|Sanitize|AntiXssEncoder)
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects the usage of untrusted data output with HttpContext.Current.Request.QueryString, which may lead to security vulnerabilities.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Untrusted Data Output: HttpContext.Current.Request.QueryString.
